&lt;li&gt;Review shop drawings and technical submittals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support resolution of technical issues and design clarifications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with code compliance and system performance reviews.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support inspections, testing, and commissioning as required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
