&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required Experience: &lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor of Science in engineering.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Active PE license.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum &lt;strong&gt;5+ years&lt;/strong&gt; of Civil engineer experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
