&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ReconCraft&lt;/strong&gt; is seeking a skilled and detail-oriented &lt;strong&gt;CNC Press Brake Operator&lt;/strong&gt; to support precision metal fabrication operations in Clackamas, Oregon. This role is responsible for setting up, programming, and operating CNC press brake equipment to produce high-quality components that meet strict engineering specifications.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate has strong experience in metal forming, the ability to interpret complex blueprints, and a commitment to maintaining tight tolerances in a fast-paced manufacturing environment. This position also plays a key role in quality control, troubleshooting, and continuous process improvement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This schedule for this position is Monday through Thursday, 4pm - 2am.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities (include but are not limited to):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operate and maintain CNC press brake equipment to perform precision forming operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Upload and run pre-programmed NC files and adjust machine settings as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Read and interpret complex engineering drawings and determine proper bend sequences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set up tooling, materials, and machine configurations for each job&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Produce parts to tight tolerances while maintaining high quality standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Inspect finished parts using precision measuring tools to ensure compliance with specifications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Troubleshoot forming issues and make real-time adjustments to ensure accuracy and efficiency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Document and report non-conforming parts and support quality control processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate production schedules, including timelines and completion estimates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow all safety procedures while working in a fast-paced manufacturing environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operate material handling equipment such as overhead cranes and forklifts (training provided)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a clean, organized, and safe work area&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
