&lt;li&gt;Must be a U.S. Citizen&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Education and Certifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High school diploma or GED required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required Experience&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5–10+ years of experience operating CNC press brake or similar forming equipment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to run complex parts independently&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of bend deduction, bend allowance, and material behavior&lt;/li&gt;
