&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Coho Construction Management&lt;/strong&gt; is seeking an experienced &lt;strong data-start=&quot;428&quot; data-end=&quot;458&quot;&gt;Commercial HVAC Technician&lt;/strong&gt; to support operations at the National Museum of the United States Army located on Fort Belvoir, Virginia. This position is responsible for the maintenance, troubleshooting, repair, and optimization of commercial and industrial HVAC&amp;amp;R systems in a secure, high-profile government environment. The ideal candidate will demonstrate strong technical expertise, professionalism, and the ability to work independently while supporting mission-critical facilities.&lt;/p&gt;
